<author>
<name>Chris Mills</name>
</author>
<content>Opera 12 brings with it a new lightweight theme system, which sits on top of the default Opera theme/skin and makes simple customisations much easier to achieve. In this article we&#39;ll take a look at how this lightweight system works.</content>
